* Please note that invoices that do not conform to our formatting and/or documentation requirements will not be processed until resubmitted correctly.

* US payments occur on Wednesdays and Fridays each week. If the 45th day falls on a Saturday, the payment window extends until Wednesday. (Bank holidays may impact check-run schedules.)

* Canadian payments are processed once per week.
